@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bkfnbe(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.69 + wp.cos(v2))
    v1 = 0.94
    v0 = v1
    tmp = (tmp - wp.exp(wp.cos(v2 + 0.89)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.42 / v0 + 0.46)) * wp.sin(0.28))
    data[tid] = v0
